docker-compose
8个组件

创建并登录UI
	注册用户 --> 注册的时候选择 worksapce （没找到 admin 管理）
	具有汉化

```
docker run -d --restart unless-stopped -p 1080:80 --network leantime-net \
-e LEAN_DB_HOST=10.1.0.81 \
-e LEAN_DB_USER=leantime \
-e LEAN_DB_PASSWORD=Inboc@2020 \
-e LEAN_DB_DATABASE=leantime \
-e LEAN_EMAIL_RETURN=chao.long@inboc.net \
--name leantime leantime/leantime:latest
```

```yaml
# Default values for leantime.
# This is a YAML-formatted file.
# Declare variables to be passed into your templates.

